<p><strong> </strong></p>
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation"><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt;">Part 1</span></strong></p>
<p dir="ltr"><span style="background-color: #f8cac6;"><strong>1. Dream and Ambition</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">What was your childhood dream?</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Are you the kind of person who sticks to dreams?</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">What is your dream job?</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Do you think you are an ambitious person?</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p dir="ltr"><span style="background-color: #f8cac6;"><strong>2. Music</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Do you prefer sad or happy music?</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Does happy music make you feel more excited?</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p dir="ltr"><span style="background-color: #f8cac6;"><strong>3. Social Media</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Have you ever posted anything on social media?</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">When did you start using social media?</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Do you think you spend too much time on social media?</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">Do your friends use social media?</p>
</li>
<li dir="ltr" aria-level="1">
<p dir="ltr" role="presentation">What do people often do on social media?</p>
